{"tid":866323,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木村光希街邊買小食 讚雞蛋仔Oishii","createTime":"2018-10-17T18:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T08:25:52.000Z","uid":160969,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c1488e1427889f14aa299edde54691a422e60c25","tid":866323,"uid":160969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T18:32:46.000Z","msg":"日本男神木村拓哉和工藤靜香的15歲細女木村光希（Koki）成為廣告界竉兒，受到許多廣告商及國際品牌追捧。被譽為最矚目星二代的Koki，昨日在星媽靜香陪伴下首度襲港，應邀來港出席品牌活動，二人抵港即吸引大批傳媒追訪，兩母女極為親民，面對傳媒時都會揮手和展現笑容。<br />\n<br />\n到港工作期間，她們更順道品嘗香港特色美食。昨日，Koki於柴灣影樓拍攝雜誌封面，靜香在社交網分享美食照，興奮介紹香港地道美食，包括雞蛋仔及蛋撻，大讚鬆脆好味，而Koki也上載食雞蛋仔等片段，並以日語大讚：「Oishii（美味）」。今日，身穿白色外套配以牛仔褲和黑色長靴的光希又同媽媽去尋找美食，見光希在店前選擇小食，最後不忘向鏡頭微笑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2yJk5C4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yJk5C4&d=qJafdh2PD12xFIro0Oi7zKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=615dc293\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2yJk5C4</a>"},{"pid":"36d0b292bf5d219facecb9d6e36d6d31e348880d","tid":866323,"uid":186711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T18:34:12.000Z","msg":"正常都會咁講"},{"pid":"d210008a0ac142a6cf3ceff701dc4fb11ddb2142","tid":866323,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"36d0b292bf5d219facecb9d6e36d6d31e348880d","tid":866323,"uid":186711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T18:34:12.000Z","msg":"正常都會咁講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T18:41:45.000Z","msg":"唔通講mazui 不味い咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814e707b1de3a1954859bd650be24eb5daf0bdb7","tid":866323,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd66e69f9ee0d53eb91032f98e0fa35b4c21db4","tid":866323,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:28:08.000Z","msg":"篇嘢係咪同阿邊撚個睇錶一樣？"},{"pid":"21772f88b521aabb5209a86887790eb630463a46","tid":866323,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:31:10.000Z","msg":"緊係讚啦 ,  話腥港小食唔好食唔驚畀兒登仔屌鳩死咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fd90998bab52b333bb40c0af90256a13b0f096","tid":866323,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v0CD5w2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv0CD5w2.jpg&h=bcf61d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EbenNK8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbenNK8.jpg&h=c6c40676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fddvWDv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfddvWDv.png&h=1d3c507b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4e0c459ffabc4110798fb19a73fa46cd09740c6","tid":866323,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f7fd90998bab52b333bb40c0af90256a13b0f096","tid":866323,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v0CD5w2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv0CD5w2.jpg&h=bcf61d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EbenNK8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbenNK8.jpg&h=c6c40676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fddvWDv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfddvWDv.png&h=1d3c507b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T08:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/162015_980afb5b2b4f65e7476b2d24ede2891d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F162015_980afb5b2b4f65e7476b2d24ede2891d.png&h=8a28b35f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2213f599be86c0b3a24bbd295f019f49